<h2 class="bold font-l">"I've got a chainsaw!"</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
In order to try and frighten off the angry mob after them, Homer attempts to fool them into thinking he has a chainsaw. With only mouth noises to go on, he does a rather unconvincing job. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/BrandishmentBluff" class='trope-example-link'>Brandishment Bluff</a></p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
